description: The Zillow Home Rental Index is Zillow's estimate of the median rental price of all homes within the neighborhood of Diamond Hill - Jarvis, Fort Worth, TX. This data is calculated by Zillow Real Estate Research (www.zillow.com/research) using their database of 110 million homes.
name: Zillow Rent Index (Neighborhoods): Rentals All Homes - Diamond Hill - Jarvis,Fort Worth,TX
